Title: Arashi Yamaha R3 High-Performance Black/Gold Front Disc & Titanium Bolts Kit - Premium Upgrade for 2015-2021 Models
Body (HTML):
Introducing the Arashi Yamaha R3 Black Front Disc - a premium performance upgrade for your motorcycle, compatible with various models from 2014-2022. Enhance your braking experience with this high-quality, durable disc rotor and titanium mounting bolts package.

Key Features:

  • Constructed from 420 stainless steel for exceptional durability
  • CNC 6061-T6 Aluminum alloy center hub for reduced weight
  • Advanced design ensures excellent heat dissipation during heavy braking
  • Minimizes brake fade, warping, and extends rotor life
  • Slotted rotor for quick water and dirt dispersion
  • Titanium Tapered Torx mounting bolts for incredible strength and corrosion resistance
  • Precision machined with CNC rolled threads for greater fatigue strength
  • Polished mirror-smooth finish for a sleek appearance

Package Includes:

  • 1 x Front Brake Disc Rotor
  • 5 x Mounting Bolts Pack
  • Installation instructions not included

Extensive Fitment List:

  • YZF R25 (2014-2021)
  • MT03 ABS (2016-2021)
  • YZF R3 (2015-2021)
  • YZF R3 ABS (2017-2021)
  • FZ-07 (2015-2016)
  • MT-07 (2014-2022)
  • MT-07 ABS (2014-2022)
  • MT-07 MOTO CAGE ABS (2014-2017)
  • MT-07 TRACER ABS (2016-2020)
  • XSR 700 ABS (2016-2019)
  • XTZ 700 TENERE (2019-2021)

Upgrade your motorcycle's braking performance today with the Arashi Yamaha R3 Black Front Disc and experience the difference.
